{"tid":1223484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）警務處處長極可能係法國間諜","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T18:02:56.000Z","uid":222925,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b18ecd3d909055ad315331e66db4ef97ec2b5a8c","tid":1223484,"uid":222925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"1999年，盧偉聰獲得刑事部推薦，被借調往法國里昂國際刑警組織秘書處出任聯絡主任，負責促進國際警務合作、統籌國際警務調查、籌辦國際會議及培育訓練、於成員國要求協助時作出回應、推行各項工作計劃及就特定的題目作出研究、就特別的執法項目成立工作小組，包括亞洲資訊科技罪行工作小組、籌辦訪問成員國的海外行程以國際刑警組織代表身份出席國際會議。2002年，盧偉聰晉升為高級警司；期間，國際刑警組織要求延長盧偉聰的任期至2002年年中，並且擢升他為亞洲及南太平洋區助理處長，為首位亞洲人出任國際刑警組織處長級職位<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%2581%25B0&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=f4ef5cae\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n想分化我地香港，請通知反修例大聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a1d5a43a0c1298f7d5735b838cddc61aa914f3","tid":1223484,"uid":106937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmlyc6%2Fvideos%2F2413922815343553%2F&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8NHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=ceb703f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2413922815343553/</a>"},{"pid":"d73a16c61270b9a58b9352ecabfaed24a90f2fc8","tid":1223484,"uid":222925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b2be49b84d4b6e24f79093f9e86928ba3355c78b","tid":1223484,"uid":222925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"push"},